ygData.messageBody:
I've seen those around. I wondered about those. I
saw them fighting ppl around the City guards. The
Guards weren't doing a thing to help or defend the
Drowned Citizens. <br><br>I wondered what they were b/c
I'd never seen them before either. But I've also
never gone down into the Sewer system for Freeport. I
figured it was just like the Greater Spirit. Never seen
one till recently-- sooooo... =)<br><br>shooman/
FatedHue out<br><br>PS... I wish I had enough money to buy
bandages to max Bind Wound. LOL. Measly 3 or 4 b/c of
using 10 free bandages from a friend and 40 silk
bandages I created myself. =)
